# 🔹 What is a Stack?

A Stack is a **linear data structure** that follows:

[
\text{LIFO} = \text{Last In First Out}
]

The element inserted last is removed first.

Example:

```text
Top
↓
30
20
10
```

If we pop:

```text
30 removed first
```

