# 🔹 Applications of Stack

---

## 1️⃣ Function Calls

Every function call creates:

👉 Activation Record (Stack Frame)

Stored in Call Stack.

---

## 2️⃣ Recursion

Recursive calls use stack.

Example:

```c
fact(5)
```

creates multiple stack frames.

📌 Very important GATE concept.

---

## 3️⃣ Expression Evaluation

Used for:

* Infix
* Prefix
* Postfix

---

# 🔹 Infix, Prefix & Postfix

---

### Infix

```text
A + B
```

Operator in middle.

---

### Prefix

```text
+ A B
```

Operator before operands.

---

### Postfix

```text
A B +
```

Operator after operands.

---

📌 Postfix evaluation is a favorite GATE topic.

---

# 🔹 Parentheses Matching

Stack used to check:

```text
( )
{ }
[ ]
```

Balanced or not.

