# 🔹 Common GATE Traps

### Trap 1

Stack follows:

✅ LIFO

NOT FIFO.

---

### Trap 2

Recursive calls use stack memory.

---

### Trap 3

Underflow occurs on pop from empty stack.

---

### Trap 4

Overflow occurs in array implementation only when array is full.

